{"comments":"Roughness - surface roughness for PBR materials.\n\nRange: 0.0 to 1.0 (clamps)\n- **0.0**: Perfectly smooth (mirror-like reflections)\n- **0.3**: Glossy (polished metal, wet surfaces)\n- **0.7**: Rough (concrete, fabric)\n- **1.0**: Completely diffuse (matte, no specular)\n\nControls microfacet distribution in PBR shading models (GGX, Beckmann).\nUsed in Unreal, Unity, Cinema4D, Blender, Arnold, etc.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[42,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[42,1]},"title":"eqRoughness"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[43,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[43,1]},"title":"ordRoughness"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Roughness"],"Roughness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[46,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Roughness.purs","start":[45,1]},"title":"showRoughness"}],"comments":"Surface roughness for PBR (0.0 to 1.0)\n\nControls how rough a surface appears. Smooth surfaces have sharp reflections,\nrough surfaces have diffuse, blurred reflections.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","decl